::KitKat::

She looked up at Megatron, "Commander, I would think a retreat would 
be in order.  We are out numbered and they aren't going to talk at 
this point.  Most of us are damaged and need repairs." She cringed as 
the pain went through her body.  She was leaking mech fluid. And the 
acid from Mosquitor was getting to her.
